{"tid":1575930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9月17日，林鄭指:警方不偏不倚，一視同仁","createTime":"2019-09-17T04:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T05:44:51.000Z","uid":24980,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f04f6ab65b268137f2c17e30ec009128f33bf9cf","tid":1575930,"uid":24980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:30:10.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】周六九龍灣淘大商場有持不同意見人士打鬥；而周日民陣遊行在警方反對下，有示威者繼續上街，並在港島多區引發衝突，兩日均有多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n對於警方被指執法不公，行政長官林鄭月娥指，絕不同意坊間這些極不公道的批評，她強調警方不偏不倚、一視同仁，又指警隊當時要處理兩批非常躁動、持不同意見的人士，工作並不容易，她非常肯定警隊的工作。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你係咪搞笑？<br />\n直播都出曬街啦！FB片都大把啦<br />\n點不偏不倚啊？冷氣房果班啊？<br />\n點一視同仁啊？黑社會同愛國分子一視同仁啊？<br />\n愛國分子打人打記者唔洗拘捕，後生仔就第一時間拘捕？</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b67d79e64667569b3abe826568202d888dfd8182","tid":1575930,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb14ed4e788340dab366f6d97f4e3c44d65174aa","tid":1575930,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:34:45.000Z","msg":"林鄭係月球定火星度吖<br />\n大家都唔係同一個平行時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c43f956ebe5db0a538c80f8f7bcb8bd828058f","tid":1575930,"uid":24980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:40:56.000Z","msg":"林鄭睇到的直播係平行時空另一世界？"},{"pid":"640c253376a1be0000c9de1e980d9852afb4f4ab","tid":1575930,"uid":3